{"tid":2341227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度再爆駭人強姦案 婦女遭5人輪姦後 報案時竟再被警察強姦","createTime":"2020-12-26T07:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T07:59:51.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee7c2b1e96268419cba2124b4971ac3a31f0c7f","tid":2341227,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"印度再現駭人聽聞的強姦案，一名35歲女子早前被五名男子強姦，她事後報警，豈料在警署再被警察強姦。事主披露事件後，警方宣佈展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發於印度北方邦的沙賈漢布（Shahjahanpur），事主表示她11月30日在住所附近，突然有5名男子從一輛私家車掩至，把她拖到車上，再載至附近一處田野輪姦她。<br />\n<br />\n事主之後往警署報案，負責的一名副督察把她帶到一間房間，不只沒有為她落案，竟然反過來也強姦她。事主再次向警方報案，終獲當地警務副總監錢德拉（Avinash Chandra）正視，下令徹查事件，並已於周三跟女事主會面。<br />\n<br />\n印度每15分鐘一宗強姦案<br />\n<br />\n印度2012年底發生巴士輪姦案，女究主慘遭姦殺棄屍，震撼全球，但當地性侵犯問題至今未有明顯改善。印度政府數據顯示，當地每15分鐘便會發生一宗強姦案，估計有更多個案還未獲報道。印度近期亦發生多宗嚴重性侵案件，9月一名19歲女子被輪姦致死，引發示威。到10月，再一名6歲女童在寓所被親戚強姦，留院10天後不治，於是激發示威持續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201226/VYDOGT2VDBBZJOG3HTYU75ZUWI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR27DS-5OW58GwplbktgJWxlc-2C6ZGX2ba-EXrWSTjb5NNwcFbhvrMNZjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201226%2FVYDOGT2VDBBZJOG3HTYU75ZUWI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR27DS-5OW58GwplbktgJWxlc-2C6ZGX2ba-EXrWSTjb5NNwcFbhvrMNZjQ&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUuyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=4d5891f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201226%2FVYDOGT2VDBBZJOG3HTYU75ZUWI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR27DS-5OW58GwplbktgJWxlc-2C6ZGX2ba-EXrWSTjb5NNwcFbhvrMNZjQ&h=661d77b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201226/VYDOGT2VDBBZJOG3HTYU75ZUWI/?utm_campaig